---
// Adezive Tirana – Faqja Kryesore
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="sq">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Adezive Tirana – Zgjidhje profesionale adezivësh për ndërtim, industri dhe shtëpi." />
  <title>Adezive Tirana – Ngjit më Mirë. Ndërto më Mirë.</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --orange: #ea580c;
      --orange-light: #fed7aa;
      --orange-dark: #9a3412;
      --gray-50: #f9fafb;
      --gray-100: #f3f4f6;
      --gray-200: #e5e7eb;
      --gray-500: #6b7280;
      --gray-700: #374151;
      --gray-900: #111827;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      color: var(--gray-900);
      background: #fff;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0 5%;
      height: 64px;
    }

    .logo { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gray-900); }
    .logo span { color: var(--orange); }

    .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gray-700); transition: color .2s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--orange); }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--orange);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background .2s;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #c2410c; }

    .btn-outline {
      border: 2px solid #fff;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: background .2s;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }

    /* mobile hamburger */
    .hamburger {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      padding: 4px;
    }
    .hamburger span {
      display: block;
      width: 24px; height: 2px;
      background: var(--gray-700);
      border-radius: 2px;
      transition: transform .3s, opacity .3s;
    }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(7px) rotate(45deg); }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(-7px) rotate(-45deg); }

    /* mobile drawer */
    .mobile-menu {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .25rem;
      position: absolute;
      top: 100%;
      left: 0; right: 0;
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
      padding: 1rem 5%;
      z-index: 49;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    }
    .mobile-menu.open { display: flex; }
    .mobile-menu a {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--gray-700);
      padding: .65rem .75rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background .2s, color .2s;
    }
    .mobile-menu a:hover { background: var(--gray-50); color: var(--orange); }
    .mobile-menu .btn-primary { text-align: center; margin-top: .5rem; padding: .75rem; border-radius: 10px; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #111827 0%, #1f2937 60%, #431407 100%);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 80px 5% 100px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -80px; right: -80px;
      width: 400px; height: 400px;
      background: var(--orange);
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: .08;
      filter: blur(60px);
    }
    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -100px; left: -100px;
      width: 500px; height: 500px;
      background: #fb923c;
      border-radius: 50%;
      opacity: .06;
      filter: blur(80px);
    }

    .hero-inner {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: center;
      max-width: 1200px;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(234,88,12,.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(234,88,12,.3);
      color: #fdba74;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero-badge .dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: #fb923c; }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .hero h1 span { color: #fb923c; }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #d1d5db;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      max-width: 520px;
    }

    .hero-actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }

    /* ── CAROUSEL ── */
    .hero-carousel {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
      aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    }

    .carousel-track {
      display: flex;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      transition: transform .5s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);
    }

    .carousel-slide {
      min-width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      padding: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .carousel-slide::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,.75) 0%, transparent 55%);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .slide-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .slide-1 .slide-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a5f 0%, #2563eb 100%); }
    .slide-2 .slide-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b1f0a 0%, #ea580c 100%); }
    .slide-3 .slide-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14532d 0%, #16a34a 100%); }
    .slide-4 .slide-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b2900 0%, #d97706 100%); }

    .slide-bg svg { width: 55%; height: 55%; opacity: .18; }

    .slide-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

    .slide-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: .6rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    }

    .slide-content h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin-bottom: .35rem; }
    .slide-content p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.75); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; }

    .carousel-btn {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      z-index: 10;
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .2s;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
    }
    .carousel-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.3); }
    .carousel-btn svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }
    .carousel-prev { left: 12px; }
    .carousel-next { right: 12px; }

    .carousel-dots {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 14px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 10;
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .carousel-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 0;
      transition: background .2s, transform .2s;
    }
    .carousel-dot.active { background: #fff; transform: scale(1.3); }

    /* ── STATS ── */
    .stats {
      background: var(--orange);
      color: #fff;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2.5rem 5%;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .stats .stat-value { font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .stats .stat-label { font-size: 0.8rem; opacity: .85; margin-top: 4px; }

    /* ── SECTIONS COMMON ── */
    section { padding: 80px 5%; }
    .section-tag {
      color: var(--orange);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: .5rem;
    }
    .section-title { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.25rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--gray-900); margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .section-sub { color: var(--gray-500); font-size: 1rem; max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.7; }

    .section-head { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }
    .section-head.center { text-align: center; }
    .section-head.center .section-sub { margin: 0 auto; }

    /* ── WHY US ── */
    .why { background: #fff; }

    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 1.75rem;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: 16px;
      transition: border-color .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover { border-color: var(--orange-light); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(234,88,12,.08); }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px;
      background: #fff7ed;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .feature-icon svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; color: var(--orange); }
    .feature-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
    .feature-card p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray-500); line-height: 1.6; }

    /* ── PRODUCTS ── */
    .products { background: var(--gray-50); }

    .categories-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; }

    .category-card { padding: 1.75rem; border-radius: 16px; transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s; display: block; }
    .category-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(0,0,0,.08); }
    .category-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0.75rem 0 0.4rem; }
    .category-card p { font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.6; opacity: .7; }
    .cat-arrow { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 1rem; display: block; }

    .cat-1 { background: #fff7ed; color: #9a3412; }
    .cat-2 { background: #eff6ff; color: #1e40af; }
    .cat-3 { background: #f0fdf4; color: #166534; }
    .cat-4 { background: #fefce8; color: #854d0e; }

    /* ── TESTIMONIALS ── */
    .testimonials { background: #fff; }

    .testimonials-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }

    .testimonial-card {
      background: var(--gray-50);
      border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.75rem;
    }
    .stars { display: flex; gap: 3px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .star { color: #f59e0b; font-size: 1rem; }
    .testimonial-card blockquote { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray-700); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .testimonial-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .75rem; }
    .avatar {
      width: 38px; height: 38px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--orange);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .author-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.875rem; }
    .author-role { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--gray-500); }

    /* ── CONTACT ── */


    /* ── CTA BANNER ── */
    .cta-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--orange) 0%, #c2410c 100%);
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 5%;
    }
    .cta-banner h2 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
    .cta-banner p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .cta-actions { display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: var(--orange); font-weight: 700; padding: .85rem 2rem; border-radius: 10px; font-size: .95rem; transition: background .2s; }
    .btn-white:hover { background: #fff7ed; }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer { background: #0f172a; color: #94a3b8; padding: 60px 5% 30px; }
    .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .footer-brand p { font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .footer-logo { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; }
    .footer-logo span { color: #fb923c; }
    .footer-col h4 { color: #fff; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .6rem; }
    .footer-col ul a { font-size: 0.85rem; transition: color .2s; }
    .footer-col ul a:hover { color: #fb923c; }
    .footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid #1e293b; padding-top: 1.5rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 0.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .75rem; }

    .social-links { display: flex; gap: .75rem; }
    .social-link {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: #1e293b;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
      color: #94a3b8;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: background .2s, color .2s, border-color .2s;
    }
    .social-link:hover { background: var(--orange); color: #fff; border-color: var(--orange); }
    .social-link svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .hero-carousel { max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .nav-cta { display: none; }
      .hamburger { display: flex; }
      .stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
.footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
      .form-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      section { padding: 60px 5%; }
      .hero { padding: 60px 5% 80px; }

      /* hero mobile tweaks */
      .hero-badge { display: none; }
      .hero-actions { flex-wrap: nowrap; }
      .hero-actions a {
        flex: 1;
        text-align: center;
        padding: .6rem 1rem !important;
        font-size: .8rem !important;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-carousel { aspect-ratio: 3/2; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <a href="#" class="logo">Adezive<span>Tirana</span></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#pse-ne">Pse Ne</a>
      <a href="#produktet">Produktet</a>
      <a href="#vleresimet">Vlerësime</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#kontakt" class="btn-primary nav-cta">Kërko Ofertë</a>
    <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Hap menunë">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>

    <!-- MOBILE MENU (inside nav so it sticks on scroll) -->
    <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
      <a href="#pse-ne" class="mobile-link">Pse Ne</a>
      <a href="#produktet" class="mobile-link">Produktet</a>
      <a href="#vleresimet" class="mobile-link">Vlerësime</a>
      <a href="#kontakt" class="btn-primary mobile-link">Kërko Ofertë</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">

      <!-- Majtas: tekst -->
      <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="dot"></span>
          Furnizuesi Nr. 1 i Adezivëve në Shqipëri
        </div>
        <h1>Ngjit më Mirë.<br/><span>Ndërto më Mirë.</span></h1>
        <p>Adezivë profesionalë për ndërtim, industri dhe specialitete — të besuar nga mijëra profesionistë në të gjithë Shqipërinë. Mbështetje teknike dhe dërgim kombëtar.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#produktet" class="btn-primary" style="padding:.85rem 2rem;font-size:.95rem;border-radius:10px;">Shiko Produktet</a>
          <a href="#kontakt" class="btn-outline">Kërko Ofertë</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Djathtas: carousel -->
      <div class="hero-carousel" id="heroCarousel">
        <div class="carousel-track" id="carouselTrack">

          <!-- Rrëshqitje 1 – Ndërtim -->
          <div class="carousel-slide slide-1">
            <div class="slide-bg">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 3.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="slide-content">
              <span class="slide-tag">Ndërtim</span>
              <h3>Adezivë Pllakash & Strukturorë</h3>
              <p>Adezivë C1/C2, membrare hidroizoluese dhe sisteme ngjitëse fasade për çdo ndërtim.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Rrëshqitje 2 – Industriale -->
          <div class="carousel-slide slide-2">
            <div class="slide-bg">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.343 3.94c.09-.542.56-.94 1.11-.94h1.093c.55 0 1.02.398 1.11.94l.149.894c.07.424.384.764.78.93.398.164.855.142 1.205-.108l.737-.527a1.125 1.125 0 011.45.12l.773.774c.39.389.44 1.002.12 1.45l-.527.737c-.25.35-.272.806-.107 1.204.165.397.505.71.93.78l.893.15c.543.09.94.56.94 1.109v1.094c0 .55-.397 1.02-.94 1.11l-.893.149c-.425.07-.765.383-.93.78-.165.398-.143.854.107 1.204l.527.738c.32.447.269 1.06-.12 1.45l-.774.773a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.449.12l-.738-.527c-.35-.25-.806-.272-1.203-.107-.397.165-.71.505-.781.929l-.149.894c-.09.542-.56.94-1.11.94h-1.094c-.55 0-1.019-.398-1.11-.94l-.148-.894c-.071-.424-.384-.764-.781-.93-.398-.164-.854-.142-1.204.108l-.738.527c-.447.32-1.06.269-1.45-.12l-.773-.774a1.125 1.125 0 01-.12-1.45l.527-.737c.25-.35.273-.806.108-1.204-.165-.397-.505-.71-.93-.78l-.894-.15c-.542-.09-.94-.56-.94-1.109v-1.094c0-.55.398-1.02.94-1.11l.894-.149c.424-.07.765-.383.93-.78.165-.398.143-.854-.108-1.204l-.526-.738a1.125 1.125 0 01.12-1.45l.773-.773a1.125 1.125 0 011.45-.12l.737.527c.35.25.807.272 1.204.107.397-.165.71-.505.78-.929l.15-.894z"/>
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="slide-content">
              <span class="slide-tag">Industriale</span>
              <h3>Epoksi & Lidhje Strukturore</h3>
              <p>Epoksi me dy komponentë, cianoacrilat dhe adezivë PU fleksibël për prodhim dhe montim.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Rrëshqitje 3 – Sealante -->
